name: Design And Print Stickers
tagline: System for creating and printing stickers
body:
### Info
System for creating and printing stickers with functionalities that include image resizing , cropping and uploading; Custom templates for users to choose and possibility for great stuff!

### Included Packages
* Jquery file upload
* iTextSharp
* Html Agility Pack
* Cropper v2.3.3 - jQuery image cropping plugin.
